<h2 id="simplecov">SimpleCov</h2>

<p>Please make sure that your project uses <a href="https://github.com/colszowka/simplecov">SimpleCov</a>. You should be able to demonstrate in you evaluation that SimpleCov reports accurate test coverage statistics at 95% coverage or above.</p>

<h2 id="version-control">Version Control</h2>

<p>Create your own Github repository for hosting your project. You do not need to fork anything. Make sure that you are working on branches, using pull requests, and committing frequently in small chunks of functionality.</p>
